title: Rocket League sales revenue worldwide 2016
summary: The statistic presents data on the Revenue of the June_2016 League sales revenue in the Rocket League as of 2016 .
The source projected that the June_2016 had 110 million U.S. dollars in the measured period .
gold: The statistic presents information on the sales revenue generated by Rocket League worldwide as of June 2016.
According to estimates , the game developed by Psyonix generated 110 million U.S. dollars in sales revenue in the presented period .
